" alt="hoSysteme Menü Hintergrund zeigt die Symbiose mit einem Overlay-Blur."/><ul class="nav-items nav-items-small"><li class=" has-sub"><a class="first-menu-normal has-sub-menu has-sub-menu-normal " href="/it-infrastruktur/"><span>IT-Infrastruktur</span><div class="nav-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 9 19" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#fff" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M.126 18.168a.5.5 0 00.682.726l.066-.062 8-9a.5.5 0 00.055-.589l-.055-.075-8-9A.5.5 0 00.073.76l.053.072L7.83 9.5.126 18.168z"></path></svg></div></a><div class="mega-menu-wrapper" tabindex="-1"><div class="mega-menu-inner lazy"><picture><source srcset="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_436a24404f.png" media="(min-width: 1080px)"><source srcset="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_1d463548f7.png" media="(min-width: 576px)"><img class="navigation-desktop-cover" loading="lazy" src="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_bc8be891c4.webp" width="768" height="432" alt="hoSysteme Menü Hintergrund zeigt die Symbiose mit einem Overlay-Blur."/></picture><div class="container"><div class="w-100"><div class="headline-block"><p class="h4">Starke Basis für Ihren digitalen Erfolg.</p><p>Von der Planung bis zum laufenden Betrieb: Wir schaffen verlässliche IT-Strukturen, die mit Ihrem Unternehmen wachsen.</p><a href="/it-infrastruktur/" class="headline-block__link">Zu unseren IT-Infrastruktur-Lösungen <span class="hdsvg-arrow-narrow-right"></span></a></div></div><div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between position-relative hover-menu-wrapper "><div class="sidebar-menu-item"><div class="back-link first-level-link"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 20" width="10" height="20"><path fill="#FFF" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M9.374 18.668a.5.5 0 01-.682.726l-.066-.062-8-9a.5.5 0 01-.055-.589l.055-.075 8-9a.5.5 0 01.801.592l-.053.072L1.67 10l7.704 8.668z"/></svg></div><ul class="second-level-menu"><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-infrastruktur/it-outsourcing/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="IT-Outsourcing" target=""><span>IT-Outsourcing</span></a></div></li><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-infrastruktur/it-kostenoptimierung/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="IT-Kostenoptimierung" target=""><span>IT-Kostenoptimierung</span></a></div></li><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-infrastruktur/cloud-rechenzentrum/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="Cloud-Rechenzentrum" target=""><span>Cloud-Rechenzentrum</span></a></div></li></ul></div><div class="header-teaser-wrapper"><div class="header-teaser"><span class="h5">IT modernisieren mit staatlicher Unterstützung</span><p>Investitionen in Ihre IT-Infrastruktur werden staatlich bezuschusst. Wir unterstützen Sie von der Auswahl bis zum Förderantrag.</p><a href="/unternehmen/it-foerderungen/" class="link link--line"><span> Mehr Infos zu Förderungen </span></a></div></div></div></div><button type="button" class="close-megamenu"><svg viewBox="0 0 38 18" width="38" height="18"><path fill="#FFF" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M36.336 17.747a1 1 0 001.452-1.363l-.124-.131-18-16a1 1 0 00-1.178-.11l-.15.11-18 16a1 1 0 001.183 1.602l.145-.108L19 2.34l17.336 15.407z"/></svg></button></div></div></li><li class=" has-sub"><a class="first-menu-normal has-sub-menu has-sub-menu-normal " href="/it-security/"><span>IT-Security</span><div class="nav-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 9 19" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#fff" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M.126 18.168a.5.5 0 00.682.726l.066-.062 8-9a.5.5 0 00.055-.589l-.055-.075-8-9A.5.5 0 00.073.76l.053.072L7.83 9.5.126 18.168z"></path></svg></div></a><div class="mega-menu-wrapper" tabindex="-1"><div class="mega-menu-inner lazy"><picture><source srcset="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_436a24404f.png" media="(min-width: 1080px)"><source srcset="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_1d463548f7.png" media="(min-width: 576px)"><img class="navigation-desktop-cover" loading="lazy" src="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_bc8be891c4.webp" width="768" height="432" alt="hoSysteme Menü Hintergrund zeigt die Symbiose mit einem Overlay-Blur."/></picture><div class="container"><div class="w-100"><div class="headline-block"><p class="h4">Sicherheit, die mitdenkt.</p><p>Ob Awareness, Audits oder Härtung – wir schützen Ihre Systeme ganzheitlich und proaktiv vor Cybergefahren.</p><a href="/it-security/" class="headline-block__link">Zu unseren IT-Security-Lösungen <span class="hdsvg-arrow-narrow-right"></span></a></div></div><div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between position-relative hover-menu-wrapper "><div class="sidebar-menu-item"><div class="back-link first-level-link"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 20" width="10" height="20"><path fill="#FFF" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M9.374 18.668a.5.5 0 01-.682.726l-.066-.062-8-9a.5.5 0 01-.055-.589l.055-.075 8-9a.5.5 0 01.801.592l-.053.072L1.67 10l7.704 8.668z"/></svg></div><ul class="second-level-menu"><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-security/it-forensik/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="IT-Forensik" target=""><span>IT-Forensik</span></a></div></li><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-security/it-security-hardening/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="IT-Security-Hardening" target=""><span>IT-Security-Hardening</span></a></div></li><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-security/it-risikomanagement/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="IT-Risikomanagement" target=""><span>IT-Risikomanagement</span></a></div></li><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-security/red-teaming/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="Red Teaming" target=""><span>Red Teaming</span></a></div></li><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-security/awareness-schulung/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="Awareness-Schulung" target=""><span>Awareness-Schulung</span></a></div></li><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/it-security/nis2/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="NIS2" target=""><span>NIS2</span></a></div></li></ul></div><div class="header-teaser-wrapper"><div class="header-teaser"><span class="h5">IT-Sicherheit staatlich gefördert</span><p>Bund und Länder fördern präventive IT-Sicherheitsmaßnahmen. Wir helfen Ihnen, die passende Förderung zu sichern und Ihre Systeme zu schützen.</p><a href="/unternehmen/it-foerderungen/" class="link link--line"><span> Mehr Infos zu Förderungen </span></a></div></div></div></div><button type="button" class="close-megamenu"><svg viewBox="0 0 38 18" width="38" height="18"><path fill="#FFF" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M36.336 17.747a1 1 0 001.452-1.363l-.124-.131-18-16a1 1 0 00-1.178-.11l-.15.11-18 16a1 1 0 001.183 1.602l.145-.108L19 2.34l17.336 15.407z"/></svg></button></div></div></li><li class=" "><a class="first-menu-normal " href="/it-healthcare/"><span>IT-Healthcare</span></a></li><li class=" has-sub"><a class="first-menu-normal has-sub-menu has-sub-menu-normal " href="/telekommunikation/"><span>Telekommunikation</span><div class="nav-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 9 19" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#fff" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M.126 18.168a.5.5 0 00.682.726l.066-.062 8-9a.5.5 0 00.055-.589l-.055-.075-8-9A.5.5 0 00.073.76l.053.072L7.83 9.5.126 18.168z"></path></svg></div></a><div class="mega-menu-wrapper" tabindex="-1"><div class="mega-menu-inner lazy"><picture><source srcset="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_436a24404f.png" media="(min-width: 1080px)"><source srcset="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_1d463548f7.png" media="(min-width: 576px)"><img class="navigation-desktop-cover" loading="lazy" src="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_bc8be891c4.webp" width="768" height="432" alt="hoSysteme Menü Hintergrund zeigt die Symbiose mit einem Overlay-Blur."/></picture><div class="container"><div class="w-100"><div class="headline-block"><p class="h4">Klar verbunden – überall erreichbar.</p><p>Mit modernen VoIP-Lösungen und Cloud-Telefonanlagen sorgen wir für reibungslose Kommunikation in Ihrem Unternehmen.</p><a href="/telekommunikation/" class="headline-block__link">Zu unseren TK-Produkten <span class="hdsvg-arrow-narrow-right"></span></a></div></div><div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between position-relative hover-menu-wrapper pe-0"><div class="sidebar-menu-item"><div class="back-link first-level-link"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 20" width="10" height="20"><path fill="#FFF" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M9.374 18.668a.5.5 0 01-.682.726l-.066-.062-8-9a.5.5 0 01-.055-.589l.055-.075 8-9a.5.5 0 01.801.592l-.053.072L1.67 10l7.704 8.668z"/></svg></div><ul class="second-level-menu"><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/telekommunikation/telefonanlagen/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="Telefonanlagen" target=""><span>Telefonanlagen</span></a></div></li></ul></div></div></div><button type="button" class="close-megamenu"><svg viewBox="0 0 38 18" width="38" height="18"><path fill="#FFF" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M36.336 17.747a1 1 0 001.452-1.363l-.124-.131-18-16a1 1 0 00-1.178-.11l-.15.11-18 16a1 1 0 001.183 1.602l.145-.108L19 2.34l17.336 15.407z"/></svg></button></div></div></li><li class=" has-sub"><a class="first-menu-normal has-sub-menu has-sub-menu-normal " href="/print-scan/"><span>Print &amp; Scan</span><div class="nav-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 9 19" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#fff" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M.126 18.168a.5.5 0 00.682.726l.066-.062 8-9a.5.5 0 00.055-.589l-.055-.075-8-9A.5.5 0 00.073.76l.053.072L7.83 9.5.126 18.168z"></path></svg></div></a><div class="mega-menu-wrapper" tabindex="-1"><div class="mega-menu-inner lazy"><picture><source srcset="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_436a24404f.png" media="(min-width: 1080px)"><source srcset="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_1d463548f7.png" media="(min-width: 576px)"><img class="navigation-desktop-cover" loading="lazy" src="/fileadmin/_processed_/e/a/csm_Menu-Background-Image%402x_bc8be891c4.webp" width="768" height="432" alt="hoSysteme Menü Hintergrund zeigt die Symbiose mit einem Overlay-Blur."/></picture><div class="container"><div class="w-100"><div class="headline-block"><p class="h4">Druckprozesse im Griff.</p><p>Wir optimieren Ihre Dokumentenworkflows und senken Kosten durch intelligentes Geräte- und Prozessmanagement.</p><a href="/print-scan/" class="headline-block__link">Zu unseren Print &amp; Scan Produkten <span class="hdsvg-arrow-narrow-right"></span></a></div></div><div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between position-relative hover-menu-wrapper pe-0"><div class="sidebar-menu-item"><div class="back-link first-level-link"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 20" width="10" height="20"><path fill="#FFF" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M9.374 18.668a.5.5 0 01-.682.726l-.066-.062-8-9a.5.5 0 01-.055-.589l.055-.075 8-9a.5.5 0 01.801.592l-.053.072L1.67 10l7.704 8.668z"/></svg></div><ul class="second-level-menu"><li class=""><div class="link-wrap"><a href="/print-scan/multifunktionsgeraete/" class="has-sub-menu-outline " title="Multifunktionsgeräte" target=""><span>Multifunktionsgeräte</span></a></div></li></ul></div></div></div><button type="button" class="close-megamenu"><svg viewBox="0 0 38 18" width="38" height="18"><path fill="#FFF" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M36.336 17.747a1 1 0 001.452-1.363l-.124-.131-18-16a1 1 0 00-1.178-.11l-.15.11-18 16a1 1 0 001.183 1.602l.145-.108L19 2.34l17.336 15.407z"/></svg></button></div></div></li><li class=" active has-sub"><a class="first-menu-normal has-sub-menu has-sub-menu-normal " href="/unternehmen/kontakt/"><span>Unternehmen</span><div class="nav-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 9 19" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#fff" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M.126 18.168a.5.5 0 00.682.726l.066-.062 8-9a.5.5 0 00.055-.589l-.055-.075-8-9A.5.5 0 00.073.76l.053.072L7.83 9.5.126 18.168z"></path></svg></div></a><div class="mega-menu-wrapper" tabindex="-1"><div class="mega-menu-inner lazy"><picture><source srcset="/file